videos.description: Baylor's Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. blocks the shot and passes the ball to Wendell Mitchell who scores off the nifty reverse layup.
videos.headline: Baylor block leads to a great reverse lay-up in transition

videos.description: 1H (0:03) BAY Jake Lindsey made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Baylor makes a last second 3-pointer to take a 10-point lead into halftime

videos.description: Oregon forward Chris Boucher gets a great pass and finishes at the rim over Baylor forward Jo Lual-Acuil Jr.
videos.headline: Boucher throws down huge alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Baylor's Johnathan Motley grabs the rebound and goes up strong for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Johnathan Motley's two-handed dunk extends Baylor's lead
